{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bcaa82f69c","title":"毛泽东对《中共中央关于处理罢工、罢课问题的指示》(修正稿)的批语和加写的话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d181bc6522","index":0,"year":1957,"month":3,"day":8,"articleId":"bcaa82f69c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"934e688f4b","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对《中共中央关于处理罢工、罢课问题的指示》(修正稿)的批语和加写的话","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bcaa82f69c"},{"id":"5c267b5929","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bcaa82f69c"},{"id":"2d592c11b1","type":"paragraph","text":"退小平办。略有修改。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bcaa82f69c"},{"id":"f26cafa1ca","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东三月八日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bcaa82f69c"},{"id":"459df9a84a","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bcaa82f69c"},{"id":"8f7dbb336e","type":"paragraph","text":"对这些分子中犯了严重错误的人应该给以适当的处罚，但是不应该开除他们，而应该不怕麻烦地教育他们，帮助他们改正错误。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bcaa82f69c"},{"id":"fb64cdd666","type":"paragraph","text":" 三","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bcaa82f69c"},{"id":"368a6b4d6c","type":"paragraph","text":"各级党委，特别是省、市和自治区一级的第一书记，对于了解工厂、学校以及报纸、刊物的思想政治动向，加强思想政治工作，解决这些方面的具体问题等项任务，应该立即抓起来，并且教会地、县两级和城市区级第一书记抓起这些工作。不应该只委托宣传部长、文教部长、教育和文化厅、局长这些同志去做而自己不去管它们。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bcaa82f69c"}],"page":{"id":"0b1b8e6dd2","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bcaa82f69c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}